    "title": "Fascinating experience",
    "rating": 5,
    "travelDate": "2025-11",
    "publishedDate": "2025-12-26",
    "text": "We very much enjoyed our tour of the crocodile farm. It was a highlight of our holiday. It was fascinating. Sue made it interactive and very interesting. I think she has inherited the farm, and she has lived with  crocs all her life! I was dubious about visiting a \"farm\" thinking it may be unpleasant for the crocs. Not the case here! Please visit. You will not get a chance like this anywhere else!",
